theory: iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, virginica) :- ('>'(PetalWidth, 1.1), not_in(PetalWidth, [1.1, 1.6]), in(PetalLength, [3.6, 4.8])). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, versicolor) :- ('>'(PetalWidth, 1.1), not_in(PetalWidth, [1.1, 1.6])). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, virginica) :- '>'(PetalWidth, 1.1). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, virginica) :- ('=<'(PetalWidth, 1.1), '>'(PetalLength, 3.6), '>'(SepalLength, 5.6)). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, setosa) :- true

iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, virginica) :- ('=<'(PetalLength, 3.6), '>'(PetalWidth, 1.1)). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, setosa) :- '=<'(PetalLength, 3.6). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, virginica) :- ('>'(PetalLength, 3.6), '>'(PetalWidth, 1.1), in(PetalLength, [3.6, 4.8])). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, versicolor) :- ('>'(PetalLength, 3.6), '>'(PetalWidth, 1.1)). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, virginica) :- true
